ABOUT

Hi, I’m Daniel.

I'm a New York City-based event photographer and videographer who creates content that drives business results for sports, fitness, and corporate brands. From high-energy fitness competitions to exclusive corporate gatherings, I capture the moments and stories that generate buzz, attract sponsors, and convert audiences.

My work transforms events into marketing assets that work long after the last guest leaves. I don't just document what happened—I create content that drives your next registration, attracts your next sponsor, and builds the community around your brand.

With experience shaped by global brands like Nike and Sotheby's, plus perspectives from Seattle to Shanghai, I understand what makes content convert. Whether it's a corporate conference or wellness gathering, I create visual assets that work as hard as you do.

I specialize in showing people what they're missing out on - turning single events into year-round marketing campaigns that drive sales, sponsorships, and community growth.

Event Photography & Video Services:

Corporate Events:

Conferences and networking events

Company retreats and team building

Product launch events

Awards ceremonies and galas

Executive portraits and headshots

Sports & Fitness Events:

Competitions and tournaments

Fitness challenges and races

Wellness gatherings and retreats

Athlete portraits and action shots

Sponsor activation coverage
